description:
Minecraft Server. Today we hop all over the server. We check out 2 new note block songs we installed for Tango and Bdubs. After a failure, the base gets a new special room installed that is definitely not another failure.

While shopping with our Sneak-E-E's loot, we stumble across the secret hush hush Mycelium Resistance HQ. An auction and a starter base at the upside-down area later... we play our first run of Tango's Decked Out mega-game.

Tango's Decked Out: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u8-e5rfKUXw

Note Block Music: 
Seiken Densetsu 3 - Little Sweet Cafe
Super Mario RPG - Sunken Ship
Twinkle Little Star
Bubble Bobble - Main Theme Remix
Final Fantasy 5 - Evil Lord Ex Death 2
Super Metroid - Lower Norfair
